  "text": "The GT power plant modeled using Aspen Hysys V8, Process simulation tool. Component validation of the simulation tool has done using the GT power plant data available in the literature [CITATION_1] . The percentage of deviation from the actual plant data and simulation model is shown in Table  3 . The maximum deviation among all the parameters is found to be less than 5%. Therefore, the simulation tool is capable of giving accurate results for GT power plants.",
